---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="เปรียบเทียบบัตรเครดิต — ดอกเบี้ย ค่าธรรมเนียม ปิดหนี้เร็ว | Kamnuanlek"
  description="เครื่องคำนวณบัตรเครดิตฟรี คำนวณดอกเบี้ย กับดักจ่ายขั้นต่ำ ระยะเวลาปิดหนี้ และเปรียบเทียบค่าธรรมเนียมรายปี บริหารหนี้บัตรเครดิตได้ฉลาดขึ้น"
>
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4">เครื่องคำนวณและคู่มือบัตรเครดิต</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12">
      Understand credit card costs and manage debt effectively. Calculate interest, payoff timeline, and annual fee value.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <a href="/คำนวณดอกเบี้ยบัตรเครดิต/" class="group p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-primary-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">💳</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-primary-600">Credit Card Interest Calculator</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Calculate how much interest you'll pay on your balance at Thailand's max 18% annual rate (1.5%/month).</p>
        <span class="text-primary-600 font-medium">Calculate Interest →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="/คำนวณจ่ายขั้นต่ำบัตรเครดิต/" class="group p-6 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-primary-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-3">⏳</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-primary-600">Minimum Payment Calculator</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">See how long it takes to pay off debt making only minimum payments. Spoiler: it's usually over 10 years.</p>
        <span class="text-primary-600 font-medium">Calculate →</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">⚠️ The Minimum Payment Trap</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Example: 50,000 THB credit card debt at 18%/year (1.5%/month), minimum payment 2%:</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-red-100 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700">27+ years</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium mt-1">Time to pay off</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-red-100 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700">127,000 THB</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium mt-1">Total interest paid</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border border-red-100 text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">3.5 years</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium mt-1">If you pay 2,000/month</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Smart Credit Card Tips</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span>
          <span><strong>Pay in full monthly</strong> — avoid interest entirely. Most cards have 30-55 day grace period.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span>
          <span><strong>Max rate is 18%/year</strong> — Thai BOT cap. Never pay more than 1.5%/month.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span>
          <span><strong>Balance transfer</strong> — Some banks offer 0% for 3-6 months on balance transfers.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">✓</span>
          <span><strong>Cashback vs points</strong> — For most people, cashback cards deliver more value.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Related Tools</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href="/เปรียบเทียบสินเชื่อ/" class="p-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-primary-500 transition-colors">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">🏦 Loan Comparison Guide</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">Personal loan vs credit card — which is better?</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/ตัวช่วยคำนวณการเงิน/" class="p-4 bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg hover:border-primary-500 transition-colors">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">💳 Financial Calculators Hub</span>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-2">All financial tools in one place</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
